♪With me around♪

289
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:12,460
(Fang Chao)

290
00:17:17,730 --> 00:17:19,290
- Hello?
- Come downstairs.

291
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:25,320
Come on, let's fight.

292
00:17:26,930 --> 00:17:28,560
Nie Chi, do you take me as a brother?

293
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:30,560
Are you taking me as a brother?

294
00:17:31,360 --> 00:17:32,880
The three of us stay together every day.

295
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,800
Now you think I'm a fool, right?

296
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:37,770
My family is not as good as yours.

297
00:17:38,210 --> 00:17:40,800
I'm not as good as you either.

298
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:44,080
You've been the best among us

299
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:45,160
since you were a kid.

300
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,050
Everyone's around you.

301
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,600
You are the best.

302
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:50,770
But Nie Chi, you know,

303
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:54,250
when you got good grades,

304
00:17:54,730 --> 00:17:56,360
I was happier than you.

305
00:17:57,250 --> 00:17:58,840
When your parents agreed you to stay

306
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,970
and go further with us,

307
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,530
I was much happier than you.

308
00:18:04,290 --> 00:18:06,210
When you can't overtake others,

309
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,800
I was even more anxious than you in my heart.

310
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,730
I thought

311
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,970
I could exchange it for sincerity.

312
00:18:12,490 --> 00:18:14,450
But now the truth tells me

313
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:17,320
that it's just my wishful thinking.

314
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:20,050
Only I am that fool, you know?

315
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:22,400
So why did you come back from Beijing?

316
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:23,970
You came back to take Lin Ge

317
00:18:23,970 --> 00:18:25,450
away from me, right?

318
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:28,320
I like Lin Ge, don't you know?

319
00:18:29,290 --> 00:18:31,800
Do you not know that I like Lin Ge?

320
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,970
Fang Chao, I have never thought

321
00:18:33,970 --> 00:18:34,810
that you liked her.

322
00:18:35,250 --> 00:18:36,560
If you're not happy right now,

323
00:18:37,050 --> 00:18:38,080
then just hit me.

324
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,970
Hit me until you feel comfortable.

325
00:18:41,290 --> 00:18:42,400
Aren't you a real man?

326
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:44,240
Hit me.

327
00:18:44,690 --> 00:18:45,530
Come on.

328
00:19:16,930 --> 00:19:17,770
Let's go.

329
00:19:20,490 --> 00:19:21,330
Go home.

330
00:19:22,080 --> 00:19:23,120
Go home and eat dumplings.

331
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:32,560
Next up in the gala

332
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:34,450
is my performance.

333
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:39,250
You must have heard of Northeast Errenzhuan.

334
00:19:40,050 --> 00:19:42,210
Next, I will sing a pop song
of Hong Kong, China.

335
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:43,530
for everyone.

336
00:19:46,360 --> 00:19:51,770
♪Dreams are hidden in the wind and rain♪

337
00:19:52,490 --> 00:19:58,160
♪Yellow face, black eyes with the same smile♪

338
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,050
♪8,000 miles♪

339
00:20:01,930 --> 00:20:03,400
Oh my gosh, I'm out of tune.

340
00:20:03,460 --> 00:20:05,630
- Start it over.
- It is not good.

341
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:16,690
There are more disappointments in life.

342
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:20,080
You can't take everything to heart.

343
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:23,050
Next time you go home,

344
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:26,010
you must bring both of them back.

345
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:27,400
Ok?

346
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:41,900
(National Ice Sports Base)

347
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:44,010
I'm so exhausted.

348
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:45,050
I'm exhausted.

349
00:20:45,530 --> 00:20:46,370
Let's go.

350
00:20:48,450 --> 00:20:50,290
Have you heard

351
00:20:50,530 --> 00:20:52,880
that we add the mixed team relay?

352
00:20:53,120 --> 00:20:54,970
This is our new opportunity to win gold.

353
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:57,250
I wonder how the coach will form the teams.

354
00:20:57,360 --> 00:20:58,770
Who will be in Tier 1?

355
00:20:58,770 --> 00:20:59,840
Do you still need to ask?

356
00:21:00,210 --> 00:21:03,210
That guy, and Wei, no doubt.

357
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:06,730
A girl pushes a boy.

358
00:21:06,730 --> 00:21:07,930
How much strength does that take?

359
00:21:08,210 --> 00:21:10,530
We have to train strength even more, huh?

360
00:21:11,490 --> 00:21:13,560
The coach will consider the weight factor.

361
00:21:13,690 --> 00:21:15,450
The weight difference between the two players

362
00:21:15,690 --> 00:21:16,920
in a regular relay cannot be too large.

363
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:19,160
It's doomed.

364
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,880
Then whoever pushes me

365
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,360
has to bounce themselves out.

366
00:21:34,770 --> 00:21:37,400
The holiday is over and the new season starts.

367
00:21:37,970 --> 00:21:40,080
Guys, the new season has started.

368
00:21:40,730 --> 00:21:43,010
Pull yourselves together and stay focused.

369
00:21:44,210 --> 00:21:46,450
Today, I'd like to introduce a new teammate.

370
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:49,160
Zhu Zhu from the Jiangnan Team.

371
00:21:49,910 --> 00:21:51,500
(When seeing Zhu Zhu again,)

372
00:21:51,930 --> 00:21:53,050
(I have been able to understand)

373
00:21:53,050 --> 00:21:55,450
(her helplessness and bitterness at that time.)

374
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:58,490
(In fact, no one is willing to be)

375
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:00,690
(an unknown stepping stone forever.)

376
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,010
(I'm also the same.)

377
00:22:02,730 --> 00:22:05,450
(But if what I face is a genius)

378
00:22:05,690 --> 00:22:07,290
(and the team honor,)

379
00:22:07,560 --> 00:22:08,530
(I'm happy to)

380
00:22:08,530 --> 00:22:11,120
(be the happy rabbit who escorts her)

381
00:22:11,290 --> 00:22:12,600
(to the finish line.)

382
00:22:15,120 --> 00:22:17,320
How is the recovery after bursitis surgery?

383
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:18,440
Not bad.

384
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:19,770
My Grand Prix results

385
00:22:19,770 --> 00:22:21,320
can prove that I wasn't bragging.

386
00:22:22,730 --> 00:22:23,770
I know a little about the matter

387
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:25,930
between you and Lin Ge.

388
00:22:26,930 --> 00:22:27,770
How about this?

389
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:31,250
I need you to hold on at least this season.

390
00:22:31,530 --> 00:22:32,690
You want to compete

391
00:22:32,690 --> 00:22:34,080
and I can give you this opportunity.

392
00:22:34,490 --> 00:22:36,080
As for whether you can seize this opportunity

393
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:37,160
and continue to stay here,

394
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:39,010
it still depends on yourself.

395
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,480
Thank you, Mr. Li.

396
00:22:40,730 --> 00:22:41,930
I will seize the opportunity well.

397
00:22:43,250 --> 00:22:44,090
Let's go eat.

398
00:22:58,840 --> 00:23:00,770
This flight delay is just too much.

399
00:23:01,690 --> 00:23:03,640
Wei, I'm too tired.

400
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:05,050
You go to bed early too.

401
00:23:18,490 --> 00:23:19,330
Wei.

402
00:23:20,530 --> 00:23:21,400
Wei.

403
00:23:25,050 --> 00:23:26,690
Lin Ge, it hurts badly.

404
00:23:29,490 --> 00:23:30,400
The disinfection is done.

405
00:23:30,770 --> 00:23:32,930
We can only wait for it to recover.

406
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,930
She has a relay tomorrow.

407
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:36,640
I advise against letting her compete.

408
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:38,290
And we can't give her painkillers.

409
00:23:38,800 --> 00:23:39,690
Not let her compete?

410
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:42,800
How did you get burnt like this?

411
00:23:43,690 --> 00:23:45,530
I just wanted to use a hot compress

412
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,290
and I didn't hold the kettle steadily.

413
00:23:47,450 --> 00:23:48,530
It spilled in an instant.

414
00:23:49,210 --> 00:23:50,490
Take a good rest.

415
00:23:51,210 --> 00:23:52,050
I...

416
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,250
The relay thing,

417
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,400
wait for Mr. Li to arrange it tomorrow.

418
00:24:12,120 --> 00:24:13,880
Why didn't you take care of Xie Lingwei?

419
00:24:15,050 --> 00:24:16,720
I was too tired. I fell asleep.

420
00:24:16,970 --> 00:24:18,490
I mentioned it to you guys before.

421
00:24:18,600 --> 00:24:20,360
Be extra cautious before the competition.

422
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,210
But her foot got burnt like this.

423
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:23,250
How can she compete now?

424
00:24:23,970 --> 00:24:26,550
Manager, am I a nanny?

425
00:24:27,050 --> 00:24:28,530
I'm also here to compete.

426
00:24:28,730 --> 00:24:30,490
Xie Lingwei has poor self-care abilities.

427
00:24:30,490 --> 00:24:32,430
How long does it take you to boil water?

428
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:34,450
Is it my fault?

429
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:35,970
Do I have to keep an eye

430
00:24:35,970 --> 00:24:36,970
on her 24 hours a day?

431
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:38,640
Don't have a fit.

432
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:40,840
I don't.

433
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,080
If I don't say it,

434
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:44,280
you may just pretend you didn't see it.

435
00:24:44,490 --> 00:24:46,290
If I say it, you'll think I'm having a fit.

436
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:48,600
The result is either I am not being sensible

437
00:24:48,690 --> 00:24:51,160
or I have to become the second Shan, right?

438
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,600
Don't put it so extreme.

439
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:54,530
Xie Lingwei is a good friend of yours.

440
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,800
This is just teammates helping each other.

441
00:24:57,060 --> 00:24:59,160
It's true that I am friends with Wei.

442
00:24:59,450 --> 00:25:00,930
I am willing to take care of her myself.

443
00:25:01,050 --> 00:25:02,080
This is one matter.

444
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:03,880
If everyone assumes

445
00:25:03,970 --> 00:25:05,320
that I have to take care of her,

446
00:25:05,540 --> 00:25:06,880
then that's another matter.

447
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:08,880
The first one is feelings.

448
00:25:09,450 --> 00:25:10,290
The second one

449
00:25:11,450 --> 00:25:12,530
is bullying.

450
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,970
Has everyone known about it now?

451
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:27,600
No.

452
00:25:27,930 --> 00:25:30,320
It's just you, Xie Lingwei

453
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:31,640
Zhu Zhu, who is going to compete tomorrow,

454
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,480
and me.

455
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:36,640
I argued with the manager.

456
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,110
Do you think I will get punished?

457
00:25:38,930 --> 00:25:40,760
Why? Are you regretting it?

458
00:25:42,730 --> 00:25:43,770
Scared?

459
00:25:46,730 --> 00:25:49,210
I'm a little scared but I don't regret it.

460
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:51,360
They were bullying me from the beginning.

461
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:53,250
Who are they?

462
00:25:54,930 --> 00:25:57,450
Those who arranged for me to be a nanny.

463
00:25:58,970 --> 00:26:01,730
Xie Lingwei annoys you every day.

464
00:26:02,010 --> 00:26:03,290
You don't seem to be angry

465
00:26:03,360 --> 00:26:04,770
and even call her Wei kindly every day.

466
00:26:04,770 --> 00:26:06,050
It's about the matter, not the person.

467
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:08,640
Wei has poor self-care abilities.

468
00:26:08,840 --> 00:26:10,740
She didn't intentionally boss me around.

469
00:26:11,560 --> 00:26:12,490
It's someone else's fault.

470
00:26:12,490 --> 00:26:15,120
This is the main reason why you feel wronged.

471
00:26:18,600 --> 00:26:19,440
You try

472
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:23,120
to learn from Gao Kai and me.

473
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:25,530
This isn't good, is it?

474
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,320
What's wrong with that?

475
00:26:27,320 --> 00:26:28,770
If you have to say it, then say it.

476
00:26:28,770 --> 00:26:30,490
At least you feel comfortable, don't you?

477
00:26:31,450 --> 00:26:33,880
Thank you, Jinting. I feel much better.

478
00:26:35,840 --> 00:26:38,160
Ordinary people like us shouldn't be led

479
00:26:38,210 --> 00:26:40,080
by the nose by geniuses.

480
00:26:40,490 --> 00:26:44,160
I think your anger was completely justified.

481
00:26:44,530 --> 00:26:46,400
At least when they manage you later,

482
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:47,690
they should think about it.

483
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:50,120
And there are so many competitions.

484
00:26:50,210 --> 00:26:52,730
These geniuses can't take all of them, huh?

485
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:57,250
Jinting, you're so insightful.

486
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,880
How could you be an ordinary person?

487
00:26:59,690 --> 00:27:01,120
I am

488
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,800
an ordinary person.

489
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:07,640
All right, stop thinking so much.

490
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:08,690
Go to bed early.

491
00:27:09,770 --> 00:27:10,610
I'm off.

492
00:27:21,120 --> 00:27:23,010
It's fine. I have handled it.

493
00:27:23,450 --> 00:27:25,530
Let's go. It's fine.

494
00:27:28,530 --> 00:27:29,490
It's the last lap of the relay

495
00:27:29,490 --> 00:27:31,120
for the World Tour Shanghai Station.

496
00:27:31,250 --> 00:27:32,120
Lin Ge, sprint!

497
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,730
Lin Ge, the rhythm.

498
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:36,100
(Post-match Press Conference)

499
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:37,160
Hello, Gao Kai,

500
00:27:37,250 --> 00:27:39,120
can you give us your comments on this match?

501
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:43,290
This is a match where new and old players

502
00:27:43,290 --> 00:27:44,490
help each other.

503
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:45,600
Regarding the match results,

504
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:46,730
the team is generally satisfied.

505
00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:48,560
Thank you, Gao Kai.

506
00:27:49,450 --> 00:27:50,290
Wei,

507
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,360
we have watched your matches

508
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:52,730
several times before.

509
00:27:53,050 --> 00:27:53,970
Before today's match,

510
00:27:53,970 --> 00:27:56,160
we heard that you missed the relay race

511
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,360
due to an accidental injury.

512
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,600
Can you tell us about the specifics?

513
00:28:00,250 --> 00:28:03,250
I accidentally burned my foot yesterday.

514
00:28:03,690 --> 00:28:05,450
The coach is worried that if I take the lead,

515
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:06,970
it will affect the match greatly.

516
00:28:06,970 --> 00:28:08,160
That's why I was replaced.

517
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:10,250
But Lin Ge is already prepared,

518
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:12,400
so the team's results were not affected.

519
00:28:12,800 --> 00:28:15,080
It's rare to have such a world competition.

520
00:28:15,320 --> 00:28:17,120
Will there be regrets if you miss it?

521
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,210
A little bit.

522
00:28:20,770 --> 00:28:21,770
Ok, thank you.

523
00:28:22,500 --> 00:28:23,450
May I ask you something, Lin Ge?

524
00:28:23,730 --> 00:28:25,560
This is your first competition gold medal.

525
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,570
Do you think it's because of luck?

526
00:28:33,690 --> 00:28:35,050
All the athletes in the competition

527
00:28:35,290 --> 00:28:36,970
are capable of contending for medals.

528
00:28:39,930 --> 00:28:42,250
Each of us relies on strength,

529
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,360
not luck.

530
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:51,140
(Post-match Press Conference)

531
00:28:51,530 --> 00:28:53,010
Hurry up and edit the material.

532
00:28:53,010 --> 00:28:54,080
Organize yours quickly.

533
00:28:54,080 --> 00:28:55,510
- Post it when we get back.
- Ok.

534
00:28:56,050 --> 00:28:57,730
Congrats, Gao Kai. Goodbye.

535
00:28:57,730 --> 00:28:59,450
Congrats, bye.

536
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,240
Gao Kai,

537
00:29:03,210 --> 00:29:06,160
what Wei said is not inappropriate, isn't it?

538
00:29:08,080 --> 00:29:09,050
I'm not sure

539
00:29:09,980 --> 00:29:11,870
if someone will interpret it maliciously.

540
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:13,640
Will they?

541
00:29:15,840 --> 00:29:18,010
Whether Xie Lingwei said it or not,

542
00:29:18,210 --> 00:29:19,930
Lin Ge suddenly took her place in the relay,

543
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:21,590
people who follow her will have speculations.

544
00:29:22,050 --> 00:29:23,640
There will be conspiracy theories.

545
00:29:23,930 --> 00:29:24,800
Her words

546
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:26,970
gave these speculations a direction.

547
00:29:28,120 --> 00:29:29,250
Mr. Gao, look here.

548
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:32,400
Thank you.

549
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:35,970
Will Lin Ge be in trouble?

550
00:29:37,530 --> 00:29:38,550
Do you want to give a reminder?

551
00:29:41,100 --> 00:29:42,900
(Shanghai Station)

552
00:29:44,360 --> 00:29:47,360
Forget it. She just won the gold medal.

553
00:29:47,970 --> 00:29:49,320
Let her be happy for a while.

554
00:29:56,460 --> 00:29:57,500
(Congratulations)
Squat down.

555
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:58,590
(on achieving good results)
Lower.

556
00:29:58,590 --> 00:29:59,230
Lower. That's right.

557
00:29:59,290 --> 00:30:00,290
Include the text.

558
00:30:00,290 --> 00:30:01,360
All right.

559
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:04,800
One, two, three.

560
00:30:05,600 --> 00:30:06,800
It's done.

561
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,290
- Let me see.
- You take a look.

562
00:30:09,050 --> 00:30:09,890
Let me see.

