00:30:13,730 --> 00:30:15,250
I still need to post on my Moments.

566
00:30:15,250 --> 00:30:16,400
How should I write it then?

567
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,490
Only my head is there.

568
00:30:17,490 --> 00:30:19,080
Did I just come out of the land?

569
00:30:19,080 --> 00:30:21,450
You asked me to include the entire banner.

570
00:30:21,530 --> 00:30:22,970
If so, the person will definitely be small.

571
00:30:22,970 --> 00:30:24,800
All right, it's ok to include the text.

572
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:26,800
Give me a like on Moments.

573
00:30:27,010 --> 00:30:28,730
You're showing off every day.

574
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:32,490
How is Fang Chao doing in the national team?

575
00:30:33,210 --> 00:30:34,840
It's good for him to be able to compete.

576
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,840
It's just so-so.

577
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:37,490
How about having a drink at my place?

578
00:30:37,490 --> 00:30:38,640
Forget it.

579
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:40,080
I'm afraid your wife will hit me.

580
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:41,640
I'm leaving now.

581
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,600
All right, let's drink another day.

582
00:30:46,540 --> 00:30:49,020
(National Ice Sports Base)

583
00:30:57,080 --> 00:30:58,730
Look at this Daniel.

584
00:30:59,120 --> 00:31:00,160
He was in the lead the whole time.

585
00:31:00,450 --> 00:31:01,290
No one can overtake him.

586
00:31:01,690 --> 00:31:03,490
Indeed, he's too impressive.

587
00:31:03,490 --> 00:31:05,600
If he goes faster next time,

588
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:07,120
I can't even see his shadow.

589
00:31:07,490 --> 00:31:08,450
He is an experienced veteran.

590
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:10,120
He has much more experience than we do.

591
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:11,540
(Dad)

592
00:31:12,530 --> 00:31:13,370
Who?

593
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:15,480
My dad.

594
00:31:15,730 --> 00:31:16,580
Quick, put it on speaker.

595
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:17,730
(Dad)
I also want to talk to Master.

596
00:31:18,730 --> 00:31:19,600
Hello? Dad.

597
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:22,050
My precious son,

598
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:24,840
are you tired after a day of flying?

599
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:27,970
You must have dialed the wrong number.

600
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,050
Is this my dad?

601
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:31,050
What are you talking about?

602
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,840
Come back and let me kick your ass.

603
00:31:33,050 --> 00:31:34,800
The you'll know whether I am your dad.

604
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:35,640
Come.

605
00:31:35,730 --> 00:31:36,840
It's my dad.

606
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,400
Be serious.

607
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,320
If you talk like this,

608
00:31:39,320 --> 00:31:40,560
I will definitely know it's you.

609
00:31:40,730 --> 00:31:42,290
What's wrong with you?

610
00:31:42,560 --> 00:31:43,640
Today is not a day off either.

611
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:44,800
Why do you call me?

612
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:45,800
Is something wrong at home?

613
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:49,080
No, what could happen to us?

614
00:31:49,690 --> 00:31:52,010
Son, have you returned to your dorm?

615
00:31:52,560 --> 00:31:54,360
Don't just stay alone in the dorm.

616
00:31:54,530 --> 00:31:55,770
Go talk to your teammates.

617
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:58,730
Otherwise, chat with me or your dad.

618
00:31:59,360 --> 00:32:01,160
I'm not alone here.

619
00:32:01,840 --> 00:32:03,530
Mrs. Fang, we're all here.

620
00:32:03,970 --> 00:32:05,930
Nie Chi, Seven Gold and I.

621
00:32:06,840 --> 00:32:08,560
Fine, you go ahead.

622
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:09,770
Well,

623
00:32:09,770 --> 00:32:12,320
we'll call Fang Chao again on the weekend.

624
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:15,770
I haven't finished speaking yet.

625
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,080
I didn't even say anything.

626
00:32:17,530 --> 00:32:18,840
I haven't introduced myself yet.

627
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:22,880
What's wrong with them today?

628
00:32:23,210 --> 00:32:25,530
See? I said he's fine, right?

629
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:26,640
Then why did you call him?

630
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,730
It's not me.

631
00:32:28,970 --> 00:32:29,970
You said

632
00:32:30,250 --> 00:32:32,280
Nie Chi and Lin Ge both have medals

633
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:33,450
and they are still in a relationship.

634
00:32:33,450 --> 00:32:35,530
You're worried our son will feel lost.

635
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:37,210
Enough. Stop arguing now.

636
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,730
I am not arguing.

637
00:32:40,450 --> 00:32:41,290
Honey,

638
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:44,160
no vegetables left. Go buy some greens.

639
00:32:45,970 --> 00:32:46,970
Fine.

640
00:32:52,730 --> 00:32:54,640
Just study well.

641
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:56,530
You have no idea how much effort I put in

642
00:32:56,530 --> 00:32:57,880
to arrange this for you.

643
00:32:58,560 --> 00:33:00,160
You give up so easily.

644
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:02,490
Where can you

645
00:33:02,490 --> 00:33:04,450
find a job without a diploma now?

646
00:33:05,320 --> 00:33:06,640
How could you watch over this shop

647
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:08,210
every day like me?

648
00:33:09,290 --> 00:33:11,080
Don't arrange anything for me, ok?

649
00:33:11,530 --> 00:33:12,840
Even if you arrange it, I won't listen.

650
00:33:14,690 --> 00:33:16,160
Auntie.

651
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,490
Auntie.

652
00:33:17,490 --> 00:33:18,770
What's going on?

653
00:33:18,770 --> 00:33:21,400
Lin Ge has won a gold medal.

654
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,720
What gold medal?

655
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:25,010
It seems to be an international competition.

656
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,490
The coach even hung a banner.

657
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:29,730
She must win quite a lot of prize money.

658
00:33:29,730 --> 00:33:30,930
Of course.

659
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:33,530
I think

660
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:36,290
you were too unkind to her back then.

661
00:33:36,930 --> 00:33:38,400
If she had been well cared for by your side,

662
00:33:38,490 --> 00:33:40,800
maybe she could help Feng now.

663
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:42,240
Back then, if it weren't for me,

664
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:44,770
how would she be where she is today?

665
00:33:44,800 --> 00:33:45,970
I need to ask Mr. Fang

666
00:33:45,970 --> 00:33:47,010
and see how much

667
00:33:47,010 --> 00:33:48,050
a world champion can get.

668
00:33:49,530 --> 00:33:50,490
What are you doing?

669
00:33:51,320 --> 00:33:53,210
What does her money have to do with us?

670
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:56,010
If you can, then don't spend my money.

671
00:33:56,490 --> 00:33:58,120
You neither go to school

672
00:33:58,450 --> 00:33:59,800
nor make money.

673
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:04,050
I work so hard to save some money.

674
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:06,210
For whom?

675
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:08,080
I'm doing this for you.

676
00:34:24,820 --> 00:34:27,930
♪Tears in my heart♪

677
00:34:28,290 --> 00:34:31,570
♪I've moved on♪

678
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:35,440
♪I'm sad and restless♪

679
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:38,520
♪But I forgive you♪

680
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:41,880
♪I shouldn't have been obsessed with you♪

681
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:45,310
♪Should I leave or stay♪

682
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:49,270
♪I can give up my dignity♪

683
00:34:49,270 --> 00:34:51,340
♪That I care about♪

684
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:57,910
♪The past and former days♪

685
00:34:57,910 --> 00:35:02,250
♪All have gone♪

686
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:05,140
♪Let it go with the flow♪

687
00:35:05,140 --> 00:35:09,060
♪Memories are close at hand♪

688
00:35:09,060 --> 00:35:13,320
♪Behind those smiles with tears♪

689
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:16,240
♪Is silence♪

690
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:18,800
♪Wave my hand♪

691
