♪Perhaps after I grow up♪

692
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:33,070
♪I keep tears in the heart♪

693
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:36,880
♪Unknowingly, I already regret it♪

694
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:40,690
♪I'm sad and restless♪

695
